Description:
One of the Best Docklands Entertainers on the Market
Sophistically renovated interior with a sensational outdoor courtyard which measures 45 sqm (approx.) that is primed to be used for amazing alfresco entertaining any time of the year, this luxury two bedroom, two bathroom retreat will have you yearning to make the ultimate Docklands change.
We need to begin with the phenomenal outdoor area, which has an abundance of space along with open and covered areas perfect to enjoy come rain, hail, or shine. This sizeable area also has its own access directly to the pool. Inside through the main entry you’ll pass the renovated family bathroom and will be taken directly into the large central lounge and meals hub, with the adjoining gourmet kitchen, functionally added extra pantry area , sumptuous benchtops, breakfast bar, and upgraded stainless steel appliances.
Both bedrooms are equipped with built-in robes and have direct access to the courtyard, which includes the master bedroom with its own gorgeous renovated ensuite. Other extras include a designer main bathroom with laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom, storage cage, secure car space, and access to a pool, gym, and entertaining area.
Enjoy this excellent NewQuay Precinct location close to The District Docklands, Costco, Victoria Harbour restaurants, supermarkets, Etihad Stadium, and the 30, 75, and 86 trams.
Please contact Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
SPACIOUS AND BRIGHT
Whether you are a first home buyer or an astute investor, don’t miss out on this incredible chance to buy in the Docklands. Located on La Trobe Street where Docklands meets the CBD sits the Lacrosse Building, ideally located next to Etihad Stadium, public transport, restaurants and shopping.
This spacious, light-filled apartment has fantastic sweeping views from the CBD to the north of Melbourne, and Victoria Harbour. Enter in to the open plan living zone that includes a modern kitchen with stone bench tops and dishwasher, and floor to ceiling window presenting stunning views and providing plenty of light. Both bedrooms come with mirrored built in robes, with the master having a study nook and ensuite. The bathrooms come with clean, contemporary finishes, and a Euro-laundry in the main bathroom. A private balcony rounds out this well designed apartment.
Completing this chic Docklands apartment is split system heating & cooling, secure car space, and secure swipe &intercom entry, as well as use of the outdoor pool and gym.
Whether you’re enjoying eating out with friends, swimming, shopping, or attending sporting events at Etihad Stadium, this is low maintenance living without the price tag.

Description:
Harbour Views Enjoyed in Brand New Luxury
Ready to live a vibrant yet relaxed Docklands lifestyle in a residence that oozes luxury and style? If so, you’ve found your brand new home with this one bedroom residence perfectly positioned in the stunning Aqui Promenade development.
Situated in the ‘Gold Tower’ which sets the standard for sleek and chic living, you’ll embrace the comfortable central living and meals zone which has quality carpet flooring underfoot, with this space opening out to a balcony which further delivers views of Victoria Harbour.
A high end kitchen comes with a stone benchtop and Miele appliances. The bedroom shares the water views and is equipped with a built-in robe and a study area, while other apartment features include an impressive bathroom with rain shower, laundry facilities, reverse cycle cooling, secure intercom, secure car space and access to a 25m indoor pool, spa, sauna, gym, library, private meeting rooms, lush rooftop garden and secure on-site bicycle storage.
You’re located opposite The District Docklands with brilliant eating choices, retail outlets, and entertainment. You’re also close to IGA X-Press and Asian grocery store, waterside restaurants, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, and the 30, 75, and 86 trams.
Please contact Vicky Leong on 0452 486 860 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
A Home Above the Tree Tops
Designed by renowned architects Elenberg Fraser, the highly desired Watergate complex is centrally located in the very heart of Docklands.
Within the South Tower, this spacious 2 bedroom apartment on the 9th floor commands the best open views around with a gorgeous westerly view on the balcony, encapsulating the beautiful greenery Docklands has to offer.
The bright and light filled open plan dining and living area features floor to ceiling windows on both the East and West providing that desirable “roomy” feel. A large central kitchen with stainless steel benchtop, stylish black cabinetry and integrated Smeg appliances (including gas stove top) is a reflection of meticulous thought into the design scheme, perfect for budding chefs and entertainers.
Master bedroom with mirrored robes also consists of a study alcove and ensuite, whilst the 2nd bedroom also with mirrored robes shares the stylish central walk through bathroom.
Additional features include ducted heating and cooling, secure undercover car space, onsite building manager and security entrance, while the building facilities including a full length heated lap pool, sauna, gymnasium and residents lounge, will ensure you have everything you need at your convenience.
Perfectly located within walking distance to Woolworths, Australia Post Office, Library at the Dock, Southern Cross Station, fantastic cafes and eateries, Free Tram Zone at your doorstep, easy access to the freeway, and only a stones throw to the Melbourne CBD.

Description:
Victoria Harbour Living with Scenic Park Views
Boasting a wonderful north easterly orientation which allows for beautiful Park views along with the CBD skyline , this smart and spacious two bedroom apartment offers a peace and tranquility that is so hard to find in living within the city.
The sensational central lounge and meals zone is defined by its open and sizeable layout, with the undercover private balcony accessed via sliding doors from the main area and displays gorgeous tree views that will have a truly calming effect. The stone kitchen is also included in the lounge/meals hub and delivers stone surfaces, island bench, and stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher.
The great sized bedrooms feature fabulous privacy separated by the sleek bathroom and both come with built-in robe storage. Other property features include a storage room on the same level as the apartment that can be accessed with ease, concealed laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, video intercom, and secure car space.
Access a scenic community garden right next door, while you’re also close to The Hub @ Docklands, cafes and restaurants including Caffe Bambino, Cafenatics, The Merchant Society, and Banoi Docklands, Etihad Stadium, Docklands Park, Capital City Trail, trams, and Southern Cross Station.
Please contact Myles Johansson on 0448 031 716 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
A 36th Floor Masterpiece in Yarra’s Edge
With a breathtaking 36th floor location and enjoying a string of highlights including multiple living zones, unforgettable CBD and bay views, and three secure car spaces, this flawless and utterly sophisticated 4 bedroom (4th bed conversion) + study, 2 bathroom residence is simply magic.
You’ll love everything about this high rise oasis, from the stunning open plan design to floor-to-ceiling windows, premium carpet, stone finishes, and superior tapware. The enormous central lounge and dining zone is a pleasure to enjoy every day, with the large undercover balcony a splendid alfresco zone that offers up remarkable views of the city and marina below.
The gourmet kitchen included in the central living zone also has beautiful views to enjoy as you prepare meals, while an island bench and Miele appliances (incl. 2 wall ovens plus a steam oven and a coffee machine) will add to your cooking experience. The fully-wired theatre/media room with speakers is ideal for movie nights, meanwhile a large study area is the ultimate home office space.
Three generous bedrooms all have fantastic storage with enhanced wardrobe fit-outs, including the master bedroom which comes with a walk-in robe and brilliant double vanity ensuite. The master bedroom also has terrific Port Phillip Bay views. Other extras include a main bathroom, laundry with custom storage, ducted heating and cooling, automated blinds, secure intercom, and storage cage. Also access an on-site gym plus RekDek which includes a gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
The Yarra’s Edge precinct is a great Docklands location close to DFO Shopping and South Wharf Promenade which enjoys a plethora of bars and eateries including The General Assembly, Meat Market, The Boatbuilders Yard, Charlie Lovett, and Munich Brauhaus. You’re also close to Crown Entertainment Complex, CBD, and public transport including trams and Southern Cross Station.
Completing the ultimate lifestyle package is an opportunity to secure a Yarra River located, 13 metre Marina Berth separately.

Newly painted

Onsite manager

Description:
Conder - Newquay (Docklands), a Masterpiece
No longer a blank canvas, Newquay has evolved into an exciting place to reside and call home.
The ‘Conder”, named after artist Charles Conder, with a striking blue glass façade, is held in high regards among the residential buildings in Newquay.
A unique podium level apartment awaits buyers looking for a low level apartment capturing the promenade and the waters of the marina in full view.
This massive 74sqm 1 bed room apartment offers space galore.
Classical timber finishes and stone benchtop features in the open style kitchen with integrated stainless steel appliances incorporating an oven and gas stove top. Plenty of cupboard space is provided for. Open plan dining and living area draws you to the beautiful view through the windows, bringing the outside in. Enormous dual access bedroom with ensuite/ central bathroom adjoins the balcony perfect for relaxing.
Other features include
• Separate laundry room
• Timber floorboards
• Ducted heating and cooling
• Security entrance
• Indoor swimming pool, steam room, gymnasium and communal BBQ area
• Car park and storage cage
Close to the revamped “The District Docklands Shopping Precinct”. Exciting cinemas currently being built along with the Woolworths supermarket. Easy in easy out. Great freeway system. Free Tram Zoned and a short walk to Southern Cross Station.

Description:
Extraordinary Space and Unbelievable Penthouse Views
This rare offering is your opportunity to secure one of the most prestigious Sub Penthouse apartments in Melbourne. From the sublime quality to the stunning panoramic views this property offers the absolute pinnacle of apartment living.
It’s hard to get over the sheer amount of space on offer with this one of a kind property as well as the views which can be enjoyed from all angles including a generous balcony and two winter gardens. These views take in the tranquil Victoria Harbour, Etihad Stadium, and the iconic CBD.
This exceptional 3 bedroom + study, 2.5 bathroom north-facing residence boasts expansive living zones including an enormous lounge and generous dining room. The well-presented kitchen overlooks the dining area and boasts a long breakfast counter, walk-in butler’s pantry, and premium stainless-steel appliances.
The master retreat itself has immense space that spills into a private winter garden and parents’ retreat that could also incorporate an office with magnificent views by day and night. The walk-through dressing area and gorgeous double vanity ensuite with spa bath represent ultimate luxury.
Two further bedrooms offer excellent wardrobe storage and are serviced by the modern bathroom offering a deep bath plus powder room. Further benefits include separate laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom entry, large storage cage, three separate car spaces, and access to a gym and concierge.
Moments to cafes and eateries on Bourke Street, Victoria Harbour Promenade restaurants, The Hub @ Docklands, Docklands Park, CBD attractions, Harbour Esplanade trams, and Southern Cross Station.
A fabulous opportunity for the astute buyer so be first to view one of the finest examples of City Living.

Description:
Raising the Bar For Opulent Yarra’s Edge Living
With an unprecedented amount of stunning custom features that combine together to create a luxury masterpiece in the Yarra’s Edge complex, this breathtaking three bedroom, two bathroom apartment in ‘Tower 1’ inspires with its bespoke brilliance and memorable views.
From the stunning Corian benchtops splashed throughout to automated roller blinds, custom joinery, designer light fixtures, and everything in between, this unique 23rd floor sensation promises the world.
Step inside and be inspired by the enormous space and light through the large central living zone, which has a dedicated tiled dining area plus a generous carpeted lounge that features a bespoke entertainment unit. This large central area also features direct access to the full-length undercover balcony which showcases spectacular views of the CBD, Yarra River, and Port Phillip Bay.
The striking kitchen is truly state of the art, with Swiss-made V-ZUG appliances dominating the space which includes an induction cooktop, steam and regular ovens, and a warming drawer. The kitchen also shows off with a Miele wine fridge in the island bench, dual Fisher & Pakyel dishdrawers, electric touch drawers, and an integrated refrigerator and freezer for your convenience.
All bedrooms have brilliant bespoke joinery plus access to the full length balcony, with the exceptional master bedroom also delivering a phenomenal fully renovated ensuite which has a stylish dual vanity and divine glass wall allowing you to enjoy city vistas from the premium bathtub. This apartment also features a gorgeous central bathroom (both ensuite and bathroom with heated towel rails), accent lighting, laundry facilities, ducted heating and cooling, video intercom, storage cage, 2 secure side-by-side car spaces, and access to RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
The amazing Yarra’s Edge is a popular destination for owner-occupiers. You have the convenience of an IGA X-Press right next door, while South Wharf with all the amazing restaurants and bars as well as DFO shopping is moments away. You’re also near Crown Entertainment Complex, Capital City Trail, Polly Woodside, Spencer Street trams, and Southern Cross Station. This apartment is truly a special and unique offering that you need to see today.

Description:
Stunning Location, Stunning Home!
Situated on the 18th floor of the prestigious Victoria Point building in Docklands, this luxury apartment offers residents a picturesque home in the heart of the city.
Strategic design fully facilitates the stunning city surrounds offered by Docklands, with floor to ceiling windows in the living area and both bedrooms allowing direct indoor-outdoor interaction. All windows slide open, extending each room out to the long personal balcony. The kitchen overlooks the living area in an open plan setting, featuring a stainless-steel oven, stainless steel dishwasher, stone benchtops, and ample storage space. In pristine condition, the property is ready for its new owners to simply move in and enjoy. A neutral palette throughout serves as the perfect base for the more personal touches. Additional facilities include European-style laundry in the bathroom, integrated heating and cooling, basement parking for one car with a storage cage in the basement.
Victoria Point offers stunning facilities to its residents with a new gymnasium, concierge reception in the entry foyer and split lift areas with security level access.
Located in the heart of Docklands, one is surrounded by all that Melbourne has to offer in cuisine, bars, shopping and entertainment. Etihad Stadium is just steps away, hosting a myriad of major sporting events and international music acts. It is a short walk to the city, made even shorter by catching a free tram at the doorstep.
The capital city bike trails will take you through the heart of the city or along the Yarra River and down to the beach in just minutes, and when driving, you have quick access to the freeways, in all directions.
Seize this marvellous opportunity while you can, it won’t last long!
Call and inspect today!
Glenn Donnelly 0419 998 235

Description:
Yarra’s Edge Standout with Inspired City and Water Vistas
With a position on the 19th floor of Tower 3 in the exclusive Yarra’s Edge precinct, this unforgettable north-facing two bedroom, two bathroom apartment with astonishing views is a Docklands opportunity that is bound to be snapped up fast!
Elegance, quality, and style are words that best describe this excellent abode, which has two spacious bedrooms with built-in robes including an amazing master haven with large bathroom comprising spacious shower, separate bath and double basins. The central lounge and dining zones are stress free areas to relax, with the lounge a fantastic spot to soak in the marvelous views including the Yarra River below and CBD skyline in the distance. The large balcony is accessed via the lounge and second bedroom which is another amazing space to appreciate the river and city vistas.
The gourmet kitchen displays elegant stone finishes, a breakfast bar and stainless steel Smeg appliances. Further features include chic second bathroom, European laundry, study nook , ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom entry, and two car spaces are other apartment extras. You also have access to RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
Sitting on the banks of the Yarra River, this precinct is highly sought-after by owner-occupiers. You’re moments to South Wharf Promenade which is alive on the weekends thanks to amazing bars and restaurants, while nearby DFO Shopping, Crown Casino, transport, and the Victoria Harbour precinct are easily accessed.
